'''''Mane Devru''''' ({{lang-kn|<U+0CAE><U+0CA8><U+0CC6> <U+0CA6><U+0CC7><U+0CB5><U+0CCD><U+0CB0><U+0CC1>}}) is a 1993 Indian [[Kannada language]] [[romance film|romantic]] [[drama film|drama]] film directed and enacted by [[V. Ravichandran]] along with [[Sudharani]] pairing together for the first time. The supporting cast features [[K. S. Ashwath]], [[Tennis Krishna]], [[Disco Shanti]] among others.<ref>{{cite web |title= Mane Devru cast and crew |url= http://entertainment.oneindia.in/kannada/movies/manedevru/cast-crew.html |publisher= ''oneindia.com'' |accessdate= 27 March 2014}}</ref>

The film was a remake of [[K. Bhagyaraj]]'s Tamil blockbuster film ''[[Mouna Geethangal]]'' (1981) and was also remade in Hindi as ''[[Ek Hi Bhool]]'' (1981).<ref>[http://crazystarravichandran.webs.com/aboutme.htm About me]</ref>

== Cast ==
* [[V. Ravichandran]] as Ranganath
* [[Sudharani]] as Janaki
* [[K. S. Ashwath]] 
* [[Disco Shanti]]
* [[Tennis Krishna]]
* Umesh
* Sathyajith
* Kashi
* Venki
* Shanthamma
* Dingri Nagaraj

== Soundtrack ==
The music was composed and lyrics for the soundtrack penned by [[Hamsalekha]].<ref>{{cite web |title= Mane Devru (1993) |url= http://mio.to/album/31-_Kannada_Movie_Songs/22440-Mane_Devru/#/album/31-_Kannada_Movie_Songs/22440-Mane_Devru/ |publisher= musicindiaonline.com |accessdate= 27 March 2014}}</ref>

